@deffn Function gtk-drag-begin  (self@tie{}@code{<gtk-widget>}) (targets@tie{}@code{<gtk-target-list*>}) (actions@tie{}@code{<gdk-drag-action>}) (button@tie{}@code{int}) (event@tie{}@code{<gdk-event>}) @result{}@tie{} (ret@tie{}@code{<gdk-drag-context>})
