@deffn Function gtk-drag-check-threshold  (self@tie{}@code{<gtk-widget>}) (start_x@tie{}@code{int}) (start_y@tie{}@code{int}) (current_x@tie{}@code{int}) (current_y@tie{}@code{int}) @result{}@tie{} (ret@tie{}@code{bool})
